Jake Fruhmorgen

Though it wasn't officially labeled as a Junior Day, nonetheless Florida hosted a plethora of top prospects on Saturday, including former Clemson offensive lineman Jake Fruhmorgen , who is looking for a landing spot after transferring from the Tigers.
Fruhmorgen, who was rated by Rivals as Rivals100 member in the 2015 class, was recruited heavily by the Gators before ending up at Clemson.
Fruhmorgen expressed that he enjoyed his trip to Gainesville.
